<h2>Understanding CRM in the Martial Arts Context</h2>

<p>Customer Relationship Management in martial arts encompasses two distinct but connected functions:</p>

<h3>Lead Management</h3>

<p>Handles the pre-enrolment phase: capturing enquiries, nurturing prospects, scheduling trials, and converting interested parties into paying students. This front-end function directly impacts school growth.</p>

<h3>Student Relationship Management</h3>

<p>Addresses the post-enrolment phase: tracking engagement, identifying retention risks, managing communications, and building the long-term relationships that create lifetime students.</p>

<strong>Effective martial arts CRM integrates both functions, creating continuity from first contact through years of training.</strong>

